        <div n="949A35LD">
          <head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-949A35LD-headnote-1">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-949A35LD-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-949A35LD-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1">A <hi rend="italics">French</hi> Gentleman dining with some Company on a Fast-day, call'd for some Bacon and Eggs. The rest were very angry, and reproved him for so heinous a Sin: Whereupon he writ the following Lines <hi rend="italics">extempore</hi>.</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-949A35LD-headnote-2">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-949A35LD-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-949A35LD-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-949A35LD-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-949A35LD-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-949A35LD-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1"><l xml:id="swift-949A35LD-line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial">P<hi rend="italics">EUT on croire avec bon sens</hi></hi></l><l xml:id="swift-949A35LD-line-2" n="2">Qu'un lardon le mit en colere;</l><l xml:id="swift-949A35LD-line-3" n="3">Ou, que manger un harang</l><l xml:id="swift-949A35LD-line-4" n="4">C'est un secret pour luy plaire?</l><l xml:id="swift-949A35LD-line-5" n="5">En sa gloire envelopé</l><l xml:id="swift-949A35LD-line-6" n="6">En sa gloire envelopéSonge t'ill bien de nos soupé</l>?<l rend="center" xml:id="swift-949A35LD-line-7" n="7"><lb/><hi rend="italics">In </hi>English<hi rend="italics"> by Dean</hi> Swift.__<hi rend="display-initial">W</hi>HO can believe with common sense,</l><l xml:id="swift-949A35LD-line-8" n="8">A bacon-slice gives God offence!</l><l xml:id="swift-949A35LD-line-9" n="9">Or, how a herring hath a charm</l><l xml:id="swift-949A35LD-line-10" n="10">Almighty anger to disarm?</l><l xml:id="swift-949A35LD-line-11" n="11">Wrapt up in majesty divine,</l><l xml:id="swift-949A35LD-line-12" n="12">Does he regard on what we dine?</l></lg>
        </div>
      </div>
